1. Abstract

Data preprocessing is one of the most important steps in data analysis and machine learning. However, many beginners struggle with cleaning datasets using programming languages. This project presents Pro Data Cleaning & Visualization Studio, a desktop application developed using Python and CustomTkinter. The application allows users to load CSV and Excel datasets, clean missing values, remove duplicate records, filter data, perform searches, visualize datasets using multiple chart types, and export cleaned data without writing code.

The software provides an intuitive graphical interface suitable for students, researchers, and analysts.

2. Introduction

Data collected from various sources often contains missing values, duplicate records, inconsistent formats, and noisy information. Cleaning such datasets manually is time-consuming.

This project provides an interactive GUI that simplifies the preprocessing process and enables users to perform exploratory data analysis (EDA) efficiently.

